
### Register
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Tannistha Mishra",
    "email": "tannistha@gmail.com",
    "password": "Test@1234"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "tannistha@gmail.com",
    "password": "NewPass@5678"
}

### Get Current User (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YmE5YzEyNzU2ODk1N2NiN2UxZGQzYyIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzgzNzM0MSwiZXhwIjoxNzc0NDQyMTQxfQ.8V_9043AvjpzmyU74NXYRTi7PHhzzrCsfvUPDIMp6Ok

### Update Password
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/auth/update-password
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YmE5YzEyNzU2ODk1N2NiN2UxZGQzYyIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzgzNzM0MSwiZXhwIjoxNzc0NDQyMTQxfQ.8V_9043AvjpzmyU74NXYRTi7PHhzzrCsfvUPDIMp6Ok
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "currentPassword": "Test@1234",
    "newPassword": "NewPass@5678"
}


### ─── PHARMACY ROUTES ──────────────────────────────────────

### Get Nearby Pharmacies 
GET http://localhost:5001/api/pharmacies/nearby?lat=17.40523868197456&lng=78.47654160674658

### Get Pharmacy by ID
GET http://localhost:5001/api/pharmacies/69baa29483f098370624940f


### ─── REPORT ROUTES ────────────────────────────────────────

### Submit a Report (requires token)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/reports
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YmE5YzEyNzU2ODk1N2NiN2UxZGQzYyIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzgzNzM0MSwiZXhwIjoxNzc0NDQyMTQxfQ.8V_9043AvjpzmyU74NXYRTi7PHhzzrCsfvUPDIMp6Ok
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pharmacyId": "69baa29483f098370624940f",
    "medicineName": "Losartan 50mg",
    "genericName": "Angiotensin II receptor blocker",
    "status": "available"
}

