### Seed Pharmacies (run once, then delete the route)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/pharmacies/seed
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Apollo Pharmacy",
    "address": "Road No. 12, Banjara Hills, Hyderabad",
    "location": {
        "type": "Point",
        "coordinates": [78.4486, 17.4156]
    }

}